// 1:1 Listening Tour — Question Template
// Use these questions in your first month. Pick 3-4 per conversation.

// Context Questions
"What does your team own, and how does it connect to ours?"
"What is the most significant challenge your team is facing right now?"
"If you could change one thing about how teams collaborate, what would it be?"

// Technical Questions
"What part of the system keeps you up at night?"
"What design decision in the last year would you revisit if you could?"
"What is the most misunderstood component in our architecture?"

// Relationship Questions
"Who else should I talk to to understand this space better?"
"What do you wish the new person (me) understood about how things work here?"
"What is your favorite thing about working on this team?"

// SAP-Specific (only if the conversation warrants it)
"Have you worked with SAP systems before? How does our architecture compare?"
"What enterprise integration patterns would be most valuable for me to share?"
